{"tid":214861,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我正式宣布所有巴絲都要去做運動，唔理重訓定帶氧","createTime":"2017-04-24T04:29:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-29T15:22:06.000Z","uid":104875,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"997d964d9b7f49510af1d54f65fbc8cb04db04de","tid":214861,"uid":104875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T04:29:35.000Z","msg":"男人老狗就唔好講啦，肌肉就是一切，自從做左gym 之後，精神左，靚仔左，行路都有風，仲考試一百分添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n絲打嘅話平時無做開運動，就改變下啦，得個瘦字身型唔好睇，肥嗰啲有太多人屌啦我唔再重複，同時增左肌，新陳代謝速度快左，可以有quotas 食自己想食嘅嘢，身型又好睇左<br />\n<br />\n驚會做粗腳嘅放心，男人想就練粗都好難，女人唔會咁易，因為內分泌嘅問題。 <br />\n<br />\n最重要嘅係多左女人，係健身室嘅巴打都起勁啲，到時多左大隻型男，你地都有so, win win <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 良性循環，到時改善埋香港人下一代基因，無得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c77808eddbf489822a7c53aa5d7ee75ef1901831","tid":214861,"uid":47184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T04:31:00.000Z","msg":"練緊腹同手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95a3ca6c018274ada2ae952fc82a32826d5981ec","tid":214861,"uid":104875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T04:31:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/24/123141_f7f4e75187a91d79436f53e1eb57c2d9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F24%2F123141_f7f4e75187a91d79436f53e1eb57c2d9.jpg&h=b2070d09&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3105bc70a43ff223a35c2b18b794d1f7efada351","tid":214861,"uid":104875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T04:33:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>練緊腹同手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n全身都要練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  最好做多關節嘅動，好似squat and deadlift"},{"pid":"4bc78e4a82b51e1e0